    Copied! 
    for i in ["bmi_male_bbj.txt.gz","bmi_female_bbj.txt.gz"]:
    sumstats = gl.Sumstats(i, snpid="SNP",chrom="CHR",pos="POS",p="P")
    gl.dump_pickle(sumstats,i + ".pickle")
    for i in ["bmi_male_bbj.txt.gz","bmi_female_bbj.txt.gz"]: sumstats = gl.Sumstats(i, snpid="SNP",chrom="CHR",pos="POS",p="P") gl.dump_pickle(sumstats,i + ".pickle")
